== 發行 ==
[[獅門娛樂|獅門娛樂]]將電影定於2016年2月5日在美國上映<ref>{{cite news | last=Gettell | first=Oliver | url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/11/12/gods-of-egypt-gerard-butler-character-poster | title=Gerard Butler goes sword-and-sandals in ''Gods of Egypt'' character poster | work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] | date=2015-11-12 | accessdate=2015-11-12 | archive-date=2015-11-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151113040208/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/11/12/gods-of-egypt-gerard-butler-character-poster | dead-url=no }}</ref>，並以2D和[[RealD_戲院|RealD 3D]]格式發行<ref>{{cite web | url=https://twitter.com/GodsofEgypt | title=Gods of Egypt | work=twitter.com | publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]] | accessdate=2015-11-17 | archive-date=2015-11-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151113014023/https://twitter.com/GodsofEgypt | dead-url=no }}</ref>。獅門影業原定於2016年2月12日為上映日，後又延遲至2016年4月8日<ref>{{cite journal | last=McNary | first=Dave | url=https://variety.com/2015/film/news/power-rangers-movie-release-date-moved-january-2017-1201484922/ | title='Power Rangers' Movie Pushed Back to 2017 | journal=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date=2015-04-30 | accessdate=2015-11-12 | archive-date=2015-11-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151116123002/https://variety.com/2015/film/news/power-rangers-movie-release-date-moved-january-2017-1201484922/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>；直到2015年11月12日，才確定為2016年2月26日上映。《[[基督科學箴言報|基督科學箴言報]]》的莫莉·德里斯科爾認為，雖然本片的上映日基本上是穩定的，但仍與提前上映的《[[傲慢與偏見與殭屍_(電影)|傲慢與偏見與殭屍]]》和《[[惡棍英雄：死侍|惡棍英雄：死侍]]》競爭<ref name="driscoll">{{cite news | last=Driscoll | first=Molly | url=http://www.csmonitor.com/The-Culture/Culture-Cafe/2015/1118/Gods-of-Egypt-How-ancient-mythology-continues-to-fascinate-pop-culture | title='Gods of Egypt': How ancient mythology continues to fascinate pop culture | work=[[The_Christian_Science_Monitor|The Christian Science Monitor]] | date=2015-11-18 | accessdate=2015-11-18 | archive-date=2015-11-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151119044519/http://www.csmonitor.com/The-Culture/Culture-Cafe/2015/1118/Gods-of-Egypt-How-ancient-mythology-continues-to-fascinate-pop-culture | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
《荷魯斯之眼：王者爭霸》主要獲得了負面的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於160條專業評論，評級僅16%，平均得分3.5／10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/gods_of_egypt/ |title=Gods of Egypt (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2016-02-26 |archive-date=2017-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171220162629/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/gods_of_egypt/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分24（滿分100）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/gods-of-egypt |title=Gods of Egypt reviews |website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2016-02-26 |archive-date=2017-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171231000639/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/gods-of-egypt |dead-url=no }}</ref>，評價普遍不佳。

=== 票房 ===
在美國和加拿大，首週末票房總計為1410萬美元位居當週第二，排於《[[惡棍英雄：死侍|惡棍英雄：死侍]]》（3150萬美元）之後。

